Production User Guide

Mar 14, 2023

This guide provides you with an overview of the contents of our guide for navigating the production process. The guide is divided into three levels - Entry, Intermediate, and Advanced. Each with specific tasks that need to be performed.

Entry Level

  • Concluded Stops
  • XX Pass
  • Ad Group Inventory

Intermediate Level

  • Event Data Tool
  • Compiling XX Pass
  • Review Missed Ads
  • Clear Failed Forms

Advanced Level

  • Date Change
  • Display
  • Create Special Events
  • Additional Artists
  • Inventory Pass
